              "rowId": 32,
              "keyParts": [
                32,
                "p3",
                "verse",
                "v6",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "Michmethath. Then on the east the boundary turns around toward Taanath-shiloh and passes along beyond it on the east to Janoah,"
            },
            {
              "rowId": 33,
              "keyParts": [
                "v006_ESV_JOS_016",
                33,
                "p3",
                "verse",
                "v6",
                "plain_text"
