              "rowId": 42,
              "keyParts": [
                42,
                "p3",
                "verse",
                "v8",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "Tappuah the boundary goes westward to the brook Kanah and ends at the sea. Such is the inheritance of the tribe of the people of Ephraim by their clans,"
